wikipedia_page.main: Daniel Philip Smith (born 5 October 1989) is an English footballer who plays as a forward for Truro City. He previously played for Plymouth Argyle, Morecambe, Eastbourne Borough, Truro City, Bath City, Weymouth and Tiverton.
